In [60]:
x = np.arange(-np.pi,np.pi,0.1)
y1 = np.sin(x)
y2 = np.cos(x)
plt.plot(x,y1,label = '正弦曲线')
plt.plot(x,y2,label = '余弦曲线')

#标题
plt.title('正弦曲线和余弦曲线')

#坐标轴标签
plt.xlabel("x轴")
plt.ylabel("y轴")

#刻度范围
plt.xlim(xmin = -np.pi*1.5,xmax = np.pi*1.5)
plt.ylim(ymin = -1.2,ymax = 1.2)

#刻度标签
plt.xticks([-np.pi,-np.pi/2,0,np.pi/2,np.pi],
           ['$-\pi$','$-\pi/2$','0','$-\pi/2$','$\pi$'])
plt.yticks([-1,-0.5,0,0.5,1],
          ['-1','-0.5','0','0.5','1'])

#参考线
plt.axvline(ymin = 0,ymax = 1)

#参考区域
plt.axvline(ymin = 0,ymax = 0.5)

#图例
plt.legend()

#添加网格
plt.grid(axis = 'y')

#指向性性注释文本
plt.annotate('最小值',xy = (-np.pi/2,-1),xytext = (-np.pi/2,-0.5),arrowprops = {'arrowstyle':'->'})

#无指向性性注释文本
plt.text(x = 3,y = 0.25,s = 'y = sin(x)',bbox = {'alpha':0.2})

Text(3, 0.25, 'y = sin(x)')
